{"tid":992940,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"統戰部：讓五星紅旗高高飄揚在教堂院內　中國主教團主席：決心不負黨和政府重托","createTime":"2019-01-23T14:01:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-23T14:12:55.000Z","uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6c817c35ce5adb65ee33710c22cd2178c3168cf0","tid":992940,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T14:01:13.000Z","msg":"統戰部：讓五星紅旗高高飄揚在教堂院內　中國主教團主席：決心不負黨和政府重托<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/china/%E7%B5%B1%E6%88%B0%E9%83%A8-%E8%AE%93%E4%BA%94%E6%98%9F%E7%B4%85%E6%97%97%E9%AB%98%E9%AB%98%E9%A3%84%E6%8F%9A%E5%9C%A8%E6%95%99%E5%A0%82%E9%99%A2%E5%85%A7-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E4%B8%BB%E6%95%99%E5%9C%98%E4%B8%BB%E5%B8%AD-%E6%B1%BA%E5%BF%83%E4%B8%8D%E8%B2%A0%E9%BB%A8%E5%92%8C%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E9%87%8D%E6%89%98/?fbclid=IwAR2B6pm_CTwbnXMVdxKvclELODd7RMwkFAT2GQ_lWutc1olwSaobiWdoL9Q#.XEVsOP1ubTs.facebook\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fchina%2F%25E7%25B5%25B1%25E6%2588%25B0%25E9%2583%25A8-%25E8%25AE%2593%25E4%25BA%2594%25E6%2598%259F%25E7%25B4%2585%25E6%2597%2597%25E9%25AB%2598%25E9%25AB%2598%25E9%25A3%2584%25E6%258F%259A%25E5%259C%25A8%25E6%2595%2599%25E5%25A0%2582%25E9%2599%25A2%25E5%2585%25A7-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E6%2595%2599%25E5%259C%2598%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E5%25B8%25AD-%25E6%25B1%25BA%25E5%25BF%2583%25E4%25B8%258D%25E8%25B2%25A0%25E9%25BB%25A8%25E5%2592%258C%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E9%2587%258D%25E6%2589%2598%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2B6pm_CTwbnXMVdxKvclELODd7RMwkFAT2GQ_lWutc1olwSaobiWdoL9Q%23.XEVsOP1ubTs.facebook&d=0%2FqHyhg9rghSYbtahiOo6MVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=78970a95\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fchina%2F%25E7%25B5%25B1%25E6%2588%25B0%25E9%2583%25A8-%25E8%25AE%2593%25E4%25BA%2594%25E6%2598%259F%25E7%25B4%2585%25E6%2597%2597%25E9%25AB%2598%25E9%25AB%2598%25E9%25A3%2584%25E6%258F%259A%25E5%259C%25A8%25E6%2595%2599%25E5%25A0%2582%25E9%2599%25A2%25E5%2585%25A7-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E6%2595%2599%25E5%259C%2598%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E5%25B8%25AD-%25E6%25B1%25BA%25E5%25BF%2583%25E4%25B8%258D%25E8%25B2%25A0%25E9%25BB%25A8%25E5%2592%258C%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E9%2587%258D%25E6%2589%2598%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2B6pm_CTwbnXMVdxKvclELODd7RMwkFAT2GQ_lWutc1olwSaobiWdoL9Q%23.XEVsOP1ubTs.facebook&h=1876813b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/china/%E7%B5%B1%E6%88%B0%E9%83%A8-%E8%AE%93%E4%BA%94%E6%98%9F%E7%B4%85%E6%97%97%E9%AB%98%E9%AB%98%E9%A3%84%E6%8F%9A%E5%9C%A8%E6%95%99%E5%A0%82%E9%99%A2%E5%85%A7-%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E4%B8%BB%E6%95%99%E5%9C%98%E4%B8%BB%E5%B8%AD-%E6%B1%BA%E5%BF%83%E4%B8%8D%E8%B2%A0%E9%BB%A8%E5%92%8C%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E9%87%8D%E6%89%98/?fbclid=IwAR2B6pm_CTwbnXMVdxKvclELODd7RMwkFAT2GQ_lWutc1olwSaobiWdoL9Q#.XEVsOP1ubTs.facebook</a><br />\n<br />\n中共政權持續打壓地下教會，對官方認可教會的控制亦愈來愈強。中共統戰部副部長王作安，上星期到訪天主教最高機構天主教愛國會和天主教主教團團，要求主教帶領信徒，繼續學習「習近平新時代中國特色社會主義思想」，並落實「讓五星紅旗高高飄揚在教堂院內」，中國天主教主教團主席馬英林就稱「決心不負黨和政府的重托」。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">據《多維新聞》報道，王作安上星期四隨方天主教愛國會和主教團，王作安稱今年是中共建政70周年，希望「一會一團」帶領信眾學習「習思想」，並落實把國旗帶進教堂，「在重大節日要舉行升旗儀式，讓五星紅旗飄揚在教堂內」。<br />\n</span><br />\n他又表示去年中梵達成主教任命協議，中國將向教廷提出主教人選，由教宗確認或否決，部分過去的地下主教會讓位於政府任命的主教，王作安要求做好主教的選聖和地下主教轉化工作。<br />\n<br />\n中國天主教主教團主席馬英林就表示，不會辜負黨和政府重托，「在新一年裡，繼續在中國化發展道路上做出更大更好的成績，為建國70周年交一份滿意答卷」。 <br />\n<br />\n較早前，王作安亦曾參觀中國道教協會，亦提出要求落實「國旗進宗教活動場所」。去年7月31日，北京舉行「全國性宗教團體聯席會議」，提出在宗教活動場所升國旗的「建議」。王作安當時稱，在宗教活動場所升國旗，有利宗教界人士和信教群眾強化國家意識和公民意識。"},{"pid":"c37eab7ef0c914c0bd96b8578139a070ad27605e","tid":992940,"uid":64191,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T14:02:58.000Z","msg":"天主教但信共產黨思想，即係假神旨拜偶像<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"252656176344c6deb37f316a5404ff4833d1b664","tid":992940,"uid":162535,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"c37eab7ef0c914c0bd96b8578139a070ad27605e","tid":992940,"uid":64191,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-23T14:02:58.000Z","msg":"